  "texts": [
    "Each supernatant sample was added to the loaded column and incubated at 4 °C for 30 min in a thermomixer.",
    "The columns were then centrifuged at 20g for 30 s and the flow waste was discarded.",
    "Resins were washed with 600 μl of wash buffer three times (50 mM NaH 2 PO 4, 300 mM NaCl, 20 mM imidazole, pH 7.4) and centrifuged at 20g for 30 s each time.",
    "Finally, the resins were incubated with 100 μl of elution buffer at 4 °C for 30 min in a thermomixer and proteins were then eluted with centrifugation at 20g for 1 min.",
    "Another 100 μl of elution buffer was added to repeat the elution steps, and the two portions of elutions were individually mixed."
  ],
